title: BREAKING: Lockdown in UK city as 'suspicious package' found
text:
Published 23rd February 2017 
Emergency services were scrambled to Manchester's Salford Quays this afternoon. 
Cops have reportedly evacuated a building in the area and roads around the Quays have been blocked off. 
A police spokesman said: "We were called shortly after 1.30pm to Anchorage Quay after a suspicious package was found. 
"Part of the building has been evacuated as a full search is conducted of the area."
